singham ( [ sɪnɡʱəm ] " lion " ) is a 2011 indian action film directed by rohit shetty , starring ajay devgn in the title role alongside kajal aggarwal and prakash raj as the antagonist . it is a remake of the 2010 tamil film singam featuring suriya and anushka shetty . the film is produced under reliance entertainment , which co-produced the original tamil movie . the theatrical trailer was released with ready in june 2011 . a sequel titled singham returns was released in august 2014 .